data.description: You won't want to miss this beautifully upgraded and very well maintained home in Mountain Shadows development in a quiet cut-de-sac.  This home features loads of upgrades from all tile floors, neutral color interior, newer window coverings, upgraded kitchen, new HVAC system, owned solar, and so much more.  Not only will you find 4 spacious bedrooms and 3 baths, you'll also find a large entry, formal dining room, breakfast nook area, living room with fireplace, family room and very spacious AZ room to sit out and enjoy.  Outside you'll find a beautiful pool and spa to enjoy along with a large covered area to sit out and enjoy the Mountain View.  The yard has been professionally landscaped and offers many fruit trees along with a fully fence back yard, circle drive and a 2.5 car garage.
